README for ~dclarke/public_html/zeus3d/gallery/simulations/problem.01

This directory contains materials from the Super-Alfvenic turbulence runs I did for a meeting I went to in Switzerland in 2010(?).  The directories containing the simulations and all the data from which these materials were gathered are scattered, and much lost.  Some data may still exist on fundy, some may be found in my "production" disc, though this was the disc that crashed and largely ended what was left of my research career.  Some of the lower resolution runs are in /Users/dclarke/zeus/zeus3d/version3.6/test_probs/3d/supaturb.

DAC, 5/16.
